<p><b><h3 class = "text-center"> OREN PELEG </p></b></h3>

<p><b><small><h3 class = "text-center"> CEO </p></small></b></h3>
 

<p>Oren has been on the Board of Directors of Anytime-FitTime since 2012 and was named as Chief Executive Officer from July 2015. His previous career as Managing Director at Oaktree Capital Management, was devoted to enhancing the management of their portfolio. Prior to joining Oaktree in 2006, Oren spent eight years in the Principal Finance Group of Nomura, which subsequently became Terra Firma Capital Partners, focussing on strategy and operations and driving the post-acquisition management of portfolio companies. Previously, Oren was employed by McKinsey & Company in the United Kingdom and Italy, where he was elected to Partner in 1998. Oren has a B.Sc. in Economics from the University of London. He is fluent in Hebrew and Italian.</p>

