 <p><b><h3 class = "text-center"> June Rogers</p></b></h3>

<p><b><small><h3 class = "text-center"> CFO </p></small></b></h3>
 

<p>June joined Anytim-FitTime as our Group Chief Financial Officer on 1st January 2013. During her career she has lived and worked in Asia, Australia, the UK, America and the Middle East. For the past 4 years June has been based in Dubai as the Head of Finance for the Al Futtaim Group, with operations across the Middle East and Asia. Between 2004-2008, June was the CFO for Sydney listed Coca Cola Amatil and before CCA spent 10 years in a variety of senior roles at Cadbury Schweppes plc, including: Finance Director Global Operations based in London, CFO Americas, based in Dallas and between 1994 and 1998, Vice President Finance Asia Pacific, based in Melbourne.  In her early career June held senior roles in a variety of smaller, family owned and private equity backed companies in Europe and Asia.</p>

